Azure turned to the two Preds and looked at them with a vibrant authority.

Azure: We go now. No matter what they do, she is down for a very long
time. Her circuits are frosted with more than ice, and it will take
decades for it to thaw, no matter what they use.

He transformed into a slender and wiry techno-organic dragon form and
looked at his two escorts.
